@number_of_rows = 15 
@large_dataset = 1000
@small_dataset = 1
@max_dataset = 10000

# EaziPay File Type Testing

### Basic EaziPay Request
POST http://localhost:3001/api/generate
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: */*

{
    "fileType": "EaziPay",
    "numberOfRows": {{number_of_rows}},
    "canInlineEdit": true
}

###

### EaziPay with Specific Date Format (YYYY-MM-DD)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/generate
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: */*

{
    "fileType": "EaziPay",
    "numberOfRows": 20,
    "dateFormat": "YYYY-MM-DD",
    "hasInvalidRows": true,
    "canInlineEdit": true
}

